{"tid":1012601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防局倒掛五星旗　消防處認衰","createTime":"2019-02-07T16:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T20:36:07.000Z","uid":5195,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"082af1e581f7cfd8fd3f800f3bc2eba30eb88f3c","tid":1012601,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"今日(7日)大年初三早上10時許，有市民途經屯門浩運街3號望后石消防局時，赫然發現天台上飄揚的五星旗倒轉懸掛，應該向上的五粒星被倒轉向下。東網記者於早上11時許到場了解，只見五星旗仍然倒掛，旁邊的區旗則掛得正確，當局內消防員得悉後，隨即將倒掛的五星旗降下，再重新正確掛上。消防處發言人確認事件，表示現正向有關人員了解詳情，並會嚴肅跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190207/photo/bkn-20190207190142702-0207_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190207222250\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190207190142702-0207_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190207222250&h=86b27624&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fae1fe45224cca8a775e75237265e3d10da6aa7","tid":1012601,"uid":36178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a81997af83ed48fb8143812fee2999101cc912","tid":1012601,"uid":39209,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:57:09.000Z","msg":"好小事啫"},{"pid":"9a255f5ac9e673e60647026f75132cf4f0bfd3af","tid":1012601,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02a966cab3ab259070b5e6d74ab0207c3b8977e","tid":1012601,"uid":191579,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efe3b4f5e8a2ed9fab0ed9b26128a93ecbb228c","tid":1012601,"uid":159313,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime